This is my first project at decodelabs.
I have built a website named after the company, 'decodelabs'. I have divided the website into four sections: Home, About, Services and Contact. It has been built using HTML and CSS. While creating the website, I incorporated semantic tags such as header, main, and footer. However, it is not responsive; it is designed only for desktop.
Open it and experience the UI/UX design.
